evron Stage，而 BBC Introducing Stage 将于“下午 3 点左右”开始。</p><p>电影节表示，有关电影节共和国舞台状态的更多信息将很快发布，并感谢电影节观众的耐心等待。</p><p>您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-full-stage-times-line-up-3765102">在此处</a>查看当天剩余时间在利兹和雷丁演出的乐队和艺术家的完整阵容。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish And The Bottlemen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gerry-cinnamon">Gerry Cinnamon</a>是今年音乐节的六大主角。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">雷伊</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">,</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c"> </a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/renee-rapp">Reneé Rapp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pendulum">Pendulum</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-curry">Denzel Curry</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kenny-beats">Kenny Beats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">Nia Archives</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/two-door-cinema-club">Two Door Cinema Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Neck-Deep">Neck Deep</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wombats">The Wombats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Ashnikko">Ashnikko</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">Rachel Chinouriri</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hak-baker">Hak Baker</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a>等也预计将出演。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024"><i>请返回 NME，</i></a><i>了解雷丁和利兹 2024 的最新新闻、评论、采访、照片等。</i></p><p> <a href="htt